text: automakers need access to vehicle data
to diagnose problems and improve vehicle
safety but unique vehicle data formats
require custom data collection systems
and as vehicles advance they generate
more data making transfer to the cloud
increasingly expensive introducing aws
iot fleet wise aws iot fleet wise makes
it easy to collect transform and
transfer vehicle data to the cloud in
near real time it removes the heavy lift
of building custom data collection
systems by simplifying access to each
vehicle's unique data format intelligent
filtering capabilities transfer only
high value data signals to the cloud
which means more useful data at a lower
cost use data from aws iot fleetwise to
remotely diagnose vehicle issues in near
real time protecting against warranty
claims and recalls or use the data to
train machine learning models that
support advanced driver assistance
systems for safer vehicles
